杰西·普莱蒙因经常被误认为马特·达蒙而感到“受宠若惊” https://www.nme.com/news/film/jesse-plemons-is-flattered-to-be-frequently-mistaken-for-matt-damon-3767545?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jesse-plemons-is-很荣幸经常被误认为马特·达蒙Chris EdwardsFri, 21 Jun 2024 10:02:18 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3767545 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “当然还有更糟糕的事情”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jesse-plemons-is-flattered-to-be-frequently-mistaken-for-matt-damon-3767545">杰西·普莱蒙 (Jesse Plemons) 因经常被误认为马特·达蒙 (Matt Damon) 而“受宠若惊”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jesse-Plemons-and-Matt-Damon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>杰西·普莱蒙曾公开表示自己经常被误认为是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matt-damon">马特·达蒙</a>，并承认他觉得这种比较“很讨人喜欢”。</p><p>这位演员与他的<em>《善良》</em>联合主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emma-stone">艾玛·斯通</a>一起出现在周四（6 月 20 日）的《<em>今日</em>秀》节目中。在露面期间，主持人克雷格·梅尔文指出，多年来人们一直关注普莱蒙与<em>《心灵捕手》</em>演员的相似之处。</p><p> “仍然不是马特·达蒙，”普莱蒙开玩笑地回应道。 “是的，有一段时间[我一直在与他进行比较]，当然还有更糟糕的事情可以称呼。绝对是让人赏心悦目。但是，是的，在我的职业生涯中，我有过各种与马特·达蒙相关的绰号等等。”</p><p> “像什么？艾米丽？”斯通开玩笑地回应，提到了正在进行的对话，即<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/emma-stone-reveals-why-she-wants-to-drop-her-stage-name-3751109">她实际上更喜欢被称为她的真名艾米丽，而不是她的艺名艾玛</a>。 “就像艾米丽一样！艾米莉·达蒙，”普莱蒙斯打趣道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3767579" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3767579" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3767579" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emma-Stone-and-Jesse-Plemons.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emma-Stone-and-Jesse-Plemons.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emma-Stone-and-Jesse-Plemons-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emma-Stone-and-Jesse-Plemons-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emma-Stone-and-Jesse-Plemons-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emma-Stone-and-Jesse-Plemons-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emma-Stone-and-Jesse-Plemons-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3767579" class="wp-caption-text"> 《善意》由艾玛·斯通和杰西·普莱蒙主演。图片来源：盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>多年来，关于普莱蒙斯与达蒙的明显相似之处的讨论一直伴随着他。在 2021 年接受<a href="https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/culture/article/jesse-plemons-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国《GQ》</em></a>采访时，他开玩笑说，他发现“越来越少的人称我为‘梅斯·达蒙’”，这是粉丝在他出演 AMC 系列<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/breaking-bad"><em>《绝命毒师》</em></a>期间给他起的昵称。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518"><em>《花月杀手》的主演</em></a>最近在<em>《吉米·金梅尔</em>现场》节目中也谈到了这种比较，喜剧演员吉列尔莫·罗德里格斯误认为他是金梅尔假装的宿敌。</p><p>当深夜主持人问普莱蒙斯是否经常被误认为达蒙时，他当时告诉金梅尔：“这件事一直困扰着我一段时间。”当被问到他自己是否能看到任何相似之处时，他回答说：“我很难说——不是真的。”</p><p>他补充道：“当我年轻的时候，我的姨妈看了<em>《心灵捕手》</em> ，出于某种原因，她告诉我妈妈‘这就是杰西老了后的样子。’”他还指出，他曾经扮演过年轻版的杰西。达蒙在 2000 年电影《<em>所有漂亮的马》</em>中扮演的角色，当时普莱蒙大约 12 岁。</p><p>普莱蒙与斯通、威廉·达福、玛格丽特·库利、周洪、乔·阿尔文、马穆杜·阿西和亨特·谢弗一起主演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/emma-stone-to-reunite-with-poor-things-director-yorgos-lanthimos-on-new-film-bugonia-3757524">欧格斯·兰斯莫斯</a>的<em>《善良》</em> ，该片将于 6 月 28 日在英国上映。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jesse-plemons-is-flattered-to-be-frequently-mistaken-for-matt-damon-3767545">杰西·普莱蒙 (Jesse Plemons) 因经常被误认为马特·达蒙 (Matt Damon) 而“受宠若惊”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
